---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Button from '../components/Button.astro';
import Card from '../components/Card.astro';
---

<Layout title="Anisé">
	<div class="header-title">
		<h1>Anisé</h1>
		<p>A multipurpose Discord Bot aiming to provide Goddess of Victory: NIKKE help.</p>
		<div class="buttons">
			<Button icon="fab fa-github" text="Visit on GitHub" link="https://github.com/skuqre/anise"/>
		</div>
	</div>

	<main>
		<h2>What can she do?</h2>
		<p class="lower"><i>Not much, actually, I made this site to learn Astro. - skuqre</i></p>

		<ul role="list" class="link-card-grid">
			<Card
				icon="info"
				title="Fast Information"
				content="Anisé can get you information you need for your NIKKEs. Information from well-known sites like nikke.gg and prydwen.gg!"
			/>
			<Card
				icon="celebration"
				title="Fun"
				content="Anisé has some commands made for fun. We got cats, bond practice, and other features that may give you some fun."
			/>
			<Card
				icon="help"
				title="Need some help?"
				content="There's a WIP documentation in over there. Take a look at the various commands Anisé can do for you."
			/>
			<Card
				icon="sentiment_dissatisfied"
				title="It's not public"
				content="My poor ass does not have the resources to host Anisé. Anisé's code is open source, so one can take a look easily."
			/>
		</ul>
		<Card
			icon="build"
			title="Curious?"
			content="You can try to build the bot yourself! A full building tutorial is in the works, but most you need is Disnake and the many other packages I have forgotten to list here."
		/>
	</main>
</Layout>

<style>
	h1 {
		font-size: 4rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		line-height: 1;
		text-align: center;
		margin-top: 0.5em;
		margin-bottom: 0.5em;
	}

    .header-title {
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;

        margin: 32px 0;
        padding-top: 48px;
        padding-bottom: 48px;

        background-color: rgba(1, 1, 1, 0.3);
        background-image: url('/images/anis.gif');
        background-repeat: no-repeat;
        background-position: 20% 0;
        background-position-y: 16px;

        text-shadow: #000 0 0 8px;
    }
    .buttons {
        margin-top: 32px;
    }
	.link-card-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(24ch, 1fr));
		gap: 20px;
		padding: 0;
	}
</style>
